dc_title_s: Riparian map of properties along the Hudson River, Englewood, Palisade and Harrington Townships, New Jersey
dc_description_s: Riparian map featuring the high water lines pertaining to various individually owned and business properties along the Hudson River in Englewood, Palisade and Harrington Townships, New Jersey.|Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection|Latest date found on map is 1881; date is inferred
